<p>(Client): I want to add a shopping cart to my site. I heard that xyz cart is free, can you add that for me?</p>
<p>(Developer): Sure! That looks easy.</p>
<p>(Months and a couple thousand dollars later): Okay, I think it finally works, and is all hooked up, ready to go. I put an SSL certificate on your $15/month GoDaddy account and so now you're all safe and secure.</p>
<p>(Client): Great! I'll just check all the boxes on this PCI questionnaire and we're in business!</p>
